import './index.scss' const About = () => { return (

It's nice to meet you!

I am an Oregon State University graduate with a Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science and a Minor in Business Administration. I am actively pursuing professional opportunities in cloud software engineering and architecture.

My time at Oregon State provided me with ample experience in many development fields. I currently find myself most interested and experienced with full stack web development but am open to new opportunites.

In recent months I have switched my focus to developing knowledge in cloud based architecture and development. I have earned the AWS Solutions Architect Associate and Cloud Practitioner Certifications and plan on continuing my pursuit for more.

As a new graduate I am extremely excited to get to work and make professional connections! Please feel free to get in contact with me through my contact page or on LinkedIn.

) } export default About;
